SELECT A.ConstructionCode, C.JoutouDate, A.RequestYear, A.RequestWeek, A.RequestDestination, B.MATERIAL_NAME AS Hinban, B.CALCULATED_VALUE AS Qty FROM ( SELECT A.ConstructionCode, B.RequestYear, B.RequestWeek, B.RequestDestination
FROM ( SELECT A.* FROM HRDSQL.FlagSetting.dbo.HouseConstructionMaterials A INNER JOIN ( SELECT A.ConstructionCode, A.ExpectedHouseRaisingDate AS JoutouDate FROM HRDSQL.HRDInformationService.dbo.ConstructionSchedule A INNER JOIN HRDSQL.HRDInformationService.dbo.Constructions B ON A.ConstructionCode = B.ConstructionCode WHERE (((A.ExpectedHouseRaisingDate)>= getdate()) AND ((B.ConstructionStatus)<>1 And (B.ConstructionStatus)<>2)) ) B ON A.ConstructionCode = B.ConstructionCode WHERE A.ConstructionMaterialCode='HE' ) A LEFT JOIN ( SELECT A.* FROM HRDSQL.HRDInformationService.dbo.ShipmentRequests A INNER JOIN ( SELECT A.ConstructionCode, A.ExpectedHouseRaisingDate AS JoutouDate FROM HRDSQL.HRDInformationService.dbo.ConstructionSchedule A INNER JOIN HRDSQL.HRDInformationService.dbo.Constructions B ON A.ConstructionCode = B.ConstructionCode WHERE (((A.ExpectedHouseRaisingDate)>= getdate()) AND ((B.ConstructionStatus)<>1 And (B.ConstructionStatus)<>2)) ) B ON A.ConstructionCode = B.ConstructionCode WHERE A.ConstructionMaterialCode='HE' ) B ON A.ConstructionCode = B.ConstructionCode ) A
INNER JOIN HRDSQL4.HtiKibiroi.dbo.T_Cad_Data B ON A.ConstructionCode = B.CDNO INNER JOIN ( SELECT A.ConstructionCode, A.ExpectedHouseRaisingDate AS JoutouDate FROM HRDSQL.HRDInformationService.dbo.ConstructionSchedule A INNER JOIN HRDSQL.HRDInformationService.dbo.Constructions B ON A.ConstructionCode = B.ConstructionCode WHERE (((A.ExpectedHouseRaisingDate)>= getdate()) AND ((B.ConstructionStatus)<>1 And (B.ConstructionStatus)<>2)) ) C ON A.ConstructionCode = C.ConstructionCode WHERE B.MATERIAL_NAME Like 'CT%' ORDER BY C.JoutouDate,A.ConstructionCode,B.Material_Name
